## Power Pack Reality Contract (inherit)

- Every task's Verification command is REAL and runs on this host. "Tests pass" is not enough; it must be `pytest tests/feature/test_x.py::test_y -v` and exit 0.
- A task is `[x]` ONLY after its Verification command returns 0.
- Total `T-###` count predicts total commit count (Micro-Commit Discipline).
- Three consecutive Verification failures on the same task = STOP and surface, do not bypass.
